{"tid":2508412,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"$47任飲任食火鍋！！！","createTime":"2021-04-28T17:45:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T22:38:09.000Z","uid":46702,"like":21,"dislike":118,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"9d231217cf0f53f64bbd0ba27e7d77741f297da3","tid":2508412,"uid":46702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:45:41.000Z","msg":"去過幾次呢間野,次次都係夜晚打邊爐~因為真係好抵食,47蚊任食冇加一.埋單真係$47,雖然唔包野飲不過果度d野飲都好平~同埋都有人係門口食風等位架,建議一係早d一係遲d去就最好~<br />\n<br />\n講返d野食先~第一次去覺得40幾蚊真係唔好期望咁大,點知反而幾好wor,最正係有蝦有蠔,雖然唔係貴&amp;新鮮貨色,但已經好surprise,幾十蚊有得食仲想點ar~(不過呢期去好似冇左蠔lu)其他料都幾齊,有隻好特別好似叫做芝心丸,入面係爆漿既芝士,有d似pizza可以拉到好長果隻cheese,好得意~其他丸呀,肥牛,菜類個d都幾齊,我自己就覺得同普通酒樓分別唔大喇.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVJp3FZc4nrfZjUT9B6h6LgKMe4H9oZGs1uR91MKiaak4?filename=6pvfohY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6pvfohY.png&h=3feb2383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZeNeWWBSoW1jgBG1Eex3pBe4pYCp58HuSwD3HPAjmnDu?filename=Q2W2NKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ2W2NKE.jpg&h=0db3e149&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVFXRS4NGDfqNZmGz8ASvYvtBghCyFpDUCSgoctaD3L5c?filename=mBuoxbj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmBuoxbj.jpg&h=1aad2b6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8f07d41fa6c043068a83d49fcee45817d870d8c","tid":2508412,"uid":354439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:46:44.000Z","msg":"有冇牛柏葉 響鈴卷 娃娃菜"},{"pid":"9bdd1c084df3d57f7c9a7574e160afbe450c7187","tid":2508412,"uid":14014,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:47:15.000Z","msg":"邊間 有無咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eeada0c5a617ccfc21a3103c79991208449c109","tid":2508412,"uid":182145,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:47:17.000Z","msg":"時光機？"},{"pid":"e7670767bcf26eda35bf05c26ff8da60058e4a